{
  "name": "div_prog_frac",
  "group": "clocking",
  "spec": "UG572 Fig 3-1/3-24 fractional divider, 1/8 resolution. div_prog supplies the integer-divided clock O; a 3-bit phase accumulator (acc += FRAC each O edge) exposes its carry as FRAC_CARRY at the boundary (the +1/8 step pulse). WARNING: the doc's true two-counter / two-VCO-phase topology is NOT reproduced; this is the N/N+1 accumulator realization.",
